&lt;h4 id=&#34;631-ä¸å…¼å®¹å˜åŠ¨&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#631-ä¸å…¼å®¹å˜åŠ¨&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 6.3.1 ä¸å…¼å®¹å˜åŠ¨&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;å¦‚æœå½“å‰ä»£ç ä¸ä¸Šä¸€ä¸ªç‰ˆæœ¬ä¸å…¼å®¹ï¼Œåˆ™ Footer éƒ¨åˆ†ä»¥ &lt;code&gt;BREAKING CHANGE&lt;/code&gt;  å¼€å¤´ï¼Œåé¢æ˜¯å¯¹å˜åŠ¨çš„æè¿°ã€ä»¥åŠå˜åŠ¨ç†ç”±å’Œè¿ç§»æ–¹æ³•ã€‚&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;BREAKING CHANGE: isolate scope bindings definition has changed.

 To migrate the code follow the example below:

 Before:

 scope: &amp;#123;
   myAttr: &#39;attribute&#39;,
 &amp;#125;

 After:

 scope: &amp;#123;
   myAttr: &#39;@&#39;,
 &amp;#125;

 The removed `inject` wasn&#39;t generaly useful for directives so there should be no code using it.
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
